Get your feet under there.
Do you want me to kick him?

38
00:09:24.032 --> 00:09:26.511
You think you can kill my fucking
friends and get away with it?

39
00:09:26.631 --> 00:09:29.030
Koverchenko. mount and crank it up.

40
00:09:29.111 --> 00:09:32.008
We're gonna squash you like a grape.

41
00:09:32.031 --> 00:09:34.431
Ask him where the other rebels are.

42
00:09:46.711 --> 00:09:48.110
What did he say?

43
00:09:48.230 --> 00:09:49.510
He does not know. sir.

44
00:09:51.911 --> 00:09:53.230
Tell 'em to stop!

45
00:10:07.911 --> 00:10:09.031
