56
00:11:58.510 --> 00:12:00.110
Do you copy?

57
00:12:00.230 --> 00:12:01.910
Yes. sir.

58
00:12:02.029 --> 00:12:05.710
T5447. do you copy?
T5447. do you copy?

59
00:12:05.830 --> 00:12:08.487
What's your position?

60
00:12:08.510 --> 00:12:12.629
- Why can't they hear us?
- T5447. do you copy? T5447. do you copy?

61
00:12:14.429 --> 00:12:16.309
T5447?

62
00:13:02.509 --> 00:13:03.829
Hasaad.

63
00:13:06.710 --> 00:13:09.429
Hasaad! Hasaad!

64
00:13:11.429 --> 00:13:13.109
Hasaad.

65
00:14:41.509 --> 00:14:42.828
Sherina. Sherina.

66
00:14:42.909 --> 00:14:44.109
Run!

67
00:15:28.229 --> 00:15:29.629
Salaam. Moustafa.

68
00:17:16.308 --> 00:17:17.828
Shahzaman.

69
00:18:52.027 --> 00:18:55.204
Come in. base. T5447.

70
00:18:55.227 --> 00:18:58.908
- Haven't seen 'em since the village.
- I can't seem to raise them.

71
00:19:04.427 --> 00:19:06.907
Hey!

72
00:19:07.027 --> 00:19:08.107
Come on!

73
00:19:08.226 --> 00:19:09.507
