- I'm not sure. sir.

78
00:19:25.829 --> 00:19:29.627
The Molotov took our radio out. We
get reception. but no transmission. sir.

79
00:19:39.507 --> 00:19:43.107
Those hills must be here.

80
00:19:43.227 --> 00:19:45.907
Kandahar Road must be on
the other side of those hills. right?

81
00:19:46.028 --> 00:19:49.707
I'm not sure. sir. The garrison grid
coordinates are 31 degrees latitude...

82
00:19:49.827 --> 00:19:52.626
Samad. you're relieved of your post.

83
00:19:52.707 --> 00:19:55.107
- Give the log book to Koverchenko.
- For what reason. sir?

84
00:19:55.227 --> 00:19:57.427
Incompetence. Record it. Koverchenko.

85
00:19:57.508 --> 00:19:59.627
