- None.

86
00:19:59.708 --> 00:20:03.284
- Give yourself a battlefield commendation. Koverchenko.
- For what. sir?

87
00:20:03.307 --> 00:20:06.027
Trying to save those tankers.

88
00:20:06.106 --> 00:20:09.508
- Check this side out. Kaminski.
- To your post!

89
00:20:10.307 --> 00:20:12.909
Hey. where are you?

90
00:20:13.029 --> 00:20:15.628
Just say. "Yes. sir"
and keep out of his way.

91
00:20:15.708 --> 00:20:17.827
Okay.

92
00:20:17.907 --> 00:20:20.804
Why did that rebel we ran over
laugh at me?

93
00:20:20.827 --> 00:20:23.285
He wasn't laughing at you.
He was happy.

94
00:20:23.308 --> 00:20:26.707
Such men believe if they die in a
holy war. they will go to paradise.

95
00:20:26.827 --> 00:20:28.107
You believe that?

96
00:20:30.227 --> 00:20:32.707
After university.
I'm not sure what I believe.

97
00:20:51.308 --> 00:20:53.706
I need a woman!

98
00:20:55.106 --> 00:20:58.307
- Maybe you'll find another sheep.
- Maybe I will.

99
00:20:58.428 --> 00:21:00.403
