100
00:21:00.426 --> 00:21:02.507
Golikov put it on. sir.

101
00:21:03.626 --> 00:21:04.906
Shit!

102
00:21:10.308 --> 00:21:13.627
Come here for a second.
I got something to show you.

103
00:21:27.307 --> 00:21:28.827
Driver. back it up!

104
00:21:34.627 --> 00:21:36.907
Troops on the ridge!

105
00:21:40.306 --> 00:21:41.706
Turret power!

106
00:21:47.227 --> 00:21:49.827
Range: 3-0-0!

107
00:21:52.706 --> 00:21:56.107
- At my command!
- What's around? What's around?

108
00:21:56.227 --> 00:21:57.826
Get it out of here!

109
00:22:01.426 --> 00:22:04.226
- Ready to roll.
- Driver. forward. Go. go. go!

110
00:22:08.908 --> 00:22:10.204
Frag!

111
00:22:10.227 --> 00:22:11.427
Head's up. Samad.

112
00:22:11.507 --> 00:22:13.427
Traversing!

113
00:22:18.907 --> 00:22:20.708
Up!

114
00:22:22.027 --> 00:22:23.027
Fire!

115
00:22:23.106 --> 00:22:24.107
On the way.

116
00:22:50.426 --> 00:22:52.682
Moustafa!

117
00:22:52.705 --> 00:22:54.427
Moustafa!

118
00:23:16.106 --> 00:23:17.426
Moustafa!

119
00:25:29.226 --> 00:25:31.882
Only one drank the water.
God damn it! Samad!

120
00:25:31.905 --> 00:25:34.905
I told you to throw that
canister far away. They found it!

121
00:25:36.305 --> 00:25:39.224
At my command. gunner. frag.

122
00:25:39.305 --> 00:25:42.426
Come on. Move. move. Move it!

123
00:25:45.225 --> 00:25:46.226
Frag is up.

124
00:25:46.305 --> 00:25:47.282
Fire.

125
00:25:47.305 --> 00:25:48.625
On the way.

126
00:25:51.024 --> 00:25:52.402
Misfire.

127
00:25:52.425 --> 00:25:53.905
Go to manual.

128
00:25:56.825 --> 00:25:57.905
Misfire.

129
00:25:58.025 --> 00:25:59.025
Out of the tank!

130
00:26:21.305 --> 00:26:23.026
- What happened?
- Misfire.

131
00:26:23.105 --> 00:26:25.625
It's gonna blow. I know it's gonna blow.

132
00:26:25.705 --> 00:26:27.506
The shell looked okay to me.

133
00:26:29.626 --> 00:26:31.402
- Samad.
- Yes. sir.

134
00:26:31.425 --> 00:26:33.705
Did you touch that shell?

135
00:26:34.425 --> 00:26:36.305
Yes. sir.

136
00:26:36.425 --> 00:26:40.706
I just handed it. I handed
it to Golikov. sir. that's all.

137
00:26:40.826 --> 00:26:44.105
Misfires happen. sir.
One in every hundred rounds.

138
00:26:44.225 --> 00:26:45.424
Cook-off.

139
00:26:49.705 --> 00:26:53.225
It's the loader's responsibility to unload.

140
00:26:53.305 --> 00:26:54.825
- Golikov.
- Sir.

141
00:26:58.105 --> 00:27:00.624
Sir. I've never handled a cook-off before.

142
00:27:03.826 --> 00:27:05.826
I will do it. sir.

143
00:27:08.026 --> 00:27:11.305
He doesn't know what he's
doing. sir. Let me go in there.

144
00:27:16.305 --> 00:27:17.825
All right. Kaminski.

145
00:27:17.905 --> 00:27:19.304
Sir?

146
00:27:19.424 --> 00:27:20.425
Pinpoint the mujas.

147
00:27:20.506 --> 00:27:22.003
Yes. sir.

148
00:27:22.026 --> 00:27:23.801
- Don't take your eyes off of them.
- Yes. sir.

149
00:27:23.824 --> 00:27:25.504
- Koverchenko.
- Golikov.

150
00:28:16.505 --> 00:28:18.304
Sir. maybe I oughta do this.

151
00:28:19.305 --> 00:28:21.105
What if something happens?

152
00:28:22.624 --> 00:28:25.425
Then Kaminski will have
his first command.

153
00:28:31.424 --> 00:28:34.704
Just tell me one thing. Koverchenko.

154
00:28:34.824 --> 00:28:37.105
Why do you stick up for the Afghan?

155
00:28:38.424 --> 00:28:41.482
'Cause he's doing the best he can. sir.

156
00:28:41.505 --> 00:28:43.503
That's what worries me.

157
00:28:47.104 --> 00:28:50.624
You've got what it takes.
Koverchenko. I've seen it.

158
00:28:50.704 --> 00:28:52.824
Just keep your head on straight.

159
00:28:58.024 --> 00:29:00.082
Why don't we just turn
and fight the rebels?

160
00:29:00.105 --> 00:29:04.104
'Cause they could put a fuckin'
hole right through us with that RPG.

161
00:29:22.624 --> 00:29:24.625
Come on. Go. go.

162
00:29:26.704 --> 00:29:29.682
Come on. Come on.

163
00:29:29.705 --> 00:29:31.024
What the hell happened?

164
00:29:31.104 --> 00:29:32.424
They're gone. sir.

165
00:29:32.504 --> 00:29:34.904
Lucky bastards don't know
Samad just saved their lives.

166
00:29:35.023 --> 00:29:36.624
I didn't do anything.

167
00:29:40.505 --> 00:29:41.704
Booby-trap that round.

168
00:29:41.824 --> 00:29:43.023
Yes. sir.

169
00:29:43.104 --> 00:29:44.423
Come on.

170
00:29:44.504 --> 00:29:45.823
Driver. crank it up.

171
00:29:59.425 --> 00:30:01.424
Get us out of here. Koverchenko.

172
00:30:01.505 --> 00:30:03.025
Moving tank.

173
00:34:30.823 --> 00:34:33.823
Build a fire. sir?

174
00:34:33.903 --> 00:34:38.999
Oh. I'm sure you lost those
muja. fuck. sir.

175
00:34:39.022 --> 00:34:41.502
Tend to the track. Kaminski.

176
00:34:41.621 --> 00:34:43.302
You got it. sir.

177
00:34:49.502 --> 00:34:51.302
Oh. God.

178
00:34:52.421 --> 00:34:55.223
Let me hit that thing.

179
00:34:55.303 --> 00:34:57.600
It is called pakhtunali.

180
00:34:57.623 --> 00:34:59.302
It's the code of honor.

181
00:34:59.422 --> 00:35:01.303
Pakhtunali.

182
00:35:01.423 --> 00:35:03.223
Three obligations.

183
00:35:03.303 --> 00:35:07.103
First. milmastia. hospitality.

184
00:35:07.223 --> 00:35:08.623
Milmastia.

185
00:35:08.703 --> 00:35:12.223
Second. badal. revenge.

186
00:35:12.302 --> 00:35:14.222
Badal.

187
00:35:14.302 --> 00:35:16.702
Third. nanawatai.

188
00:35:16.822 --> 00:35:20.022
the obligation to give. um. sanctuary

189
00:35:20.103 --> 00:35:22.623
to all those who ask.

190
00:35:22.703 --> 00:35:23.822
To all?

191
00:35:23.903 --> 00:35:24.999
All.

192
00:35:25.022 --> 00:35:26.421
Even the enemy?

193
00:35:26.502 --> 00:35:27.622
All.

194
00:35:29.423 --> 00:35:31.902
What if I kill your brother.

195
00:35:32.022 --> 00:35:35.502
and you come for badal. revenge.

196
00:35:35.622 --> 00:35:38.279
and I ask for. uh. nanawatai?

197
00:35:38.302 --> 00:35:43.080
Then I would be obligated to
feed. clothe and protect you.

198
00:35:43.103 --> 00:35:46.302
That's incredibly civilized.

199
00:35:46.423 --> 00:35:47.702
What is it. nanawatai?

200
00:35:47.822 --> 00:35:49.399
Nana-watai.

201
00:35:49.421 --> 00:35:51.021
Nana-watai.

202
00:35:52.302 --> 00:35:53.999
Bread?

203
00:35:54.022 --> 00:35:55.422
Koor wadan.

204
00:36:01.822 --> 00:36:03.222
Smells like...

205
00:36:11.103 --> 00:36:14.079
When we get back. you
gotta transfer out of this tank.

206
00:36:14.102 --> 00:36:16.021
I will win his respect in time.

207
00:36:16.101 --> 00:36:19.422
Listen to me. When the
old man gets on your back.

208
00:36:19.502 --> 00:36:21.199
there's no way to shake him off.

209
00:36:21.222 --> 00:36:22.903
My dear Konstantin.

210
00:36:23.022 --> 00:36:26.022
I regard this abuse as the
price I must pay to learn.

211
00:36:27.422 --> 00:36:29.422
I love Afghanistan.

212
00:36:29.501 --> 00:36:32.902
but we are a flea in the tail of a bear.

213
00:36:33.022 --> 00:36:35.821
We must join the 20th century.

214
00:36:35.902 --> 00:36:38.221
And when Afghans accept that.

215
00:36:38.301 --> 00:36:42.103
I will be there. knowing
technology and Russian.

216
00:36:42.821 --> 00:36:44.621
So you're a patriot?

217
00:36:44.702 --> 00:36:46.479
Yes.

218
00:36:46.502 --> 00:36:49.456
Well. so was that rebel. He wanted to
keep things the way they've always been.

219
00:36:50.501 --> 00:36:52.503
I wish I believed in something that much.

220
00:36:52.623 --> 00:36:54.703
I envy him.

221
00:36:54.823 --> 00:36:57.502
Then why did you crush him?

222
00:36:57.622 --> 00:37:00.279
Because I had no choice.

223
00:37:00.302 --> 00:37:02.199
- You always have a choice.
- Give it. Kaminski!

224
00:37:02.222 --> 00:37:04.503
You never told me she
sent you nudes of herself.

225
00:37:04.622 --> 00:37:06.502
Give it to me. Kaminski.

226
00:37:06.622 --> 00:37:08.823
Whoa. she's got that nympho look.

227
00:37:12.221 --> 00:37:14.822
Well. I got the half I want.

228
00:37:20.502 --> 00:37:22.302
Ah. you son of a bitch!

229
00:37:22.422 --> 00:37:23.421
Back off me!

230
00:37:24.821 --> 00:37:27.222
Okay. Okay. Huh?

231
00:37:27.302 --> 00:37:30.421
- What the hell is going on?
- Nothing. sir.

232
00:37:35.620 --> 00:37:37.421
Thanks. Konstantin.

233
00:37:48.100 --> 00:37:49.500
What is this?

234
00:37:54.223 --> 00:37:56.000
Brake fluid?

235
00:37:56.023 --> 00:37:58.502
No wonder they don't work.

236
00:37:58.622 --> 00:38:00.678
Keeps me steady on the guns. sir.

237
00:38:00.701 --> 00:38:03.503
I filter it through bread. you
know. to get out all the shit.

238
00:38:03.622 --> 00:38:06.479
And then I put in raisins and
sugar and I put it out in the sun.

239
00:38:06.502 --> 00:38:10.622
And it ferments in a couple
days and gets a pretty good kick.

240
00:38:14.221 --> 00:38:15.798
Write him up. sir?

241
00:38:15.821 --> 00:38:17.622
Get over here.

242
00:38:22.421 --> 00:38:23.901
For one mistake?

243
00:38:24.021 --> 00:38:28.021
He's the best gunner in
the division. Omit it.

244
00:38:28.102 --> 00:38:30.701
It's already done. sir. in ink.

245
00:39:11.620 --> 00:39:15.502
You know. you better watch your
ass from now on. Koverchenko.

246
00:39:15.622 --> 00:39:20.420
Sometimes Afghan snipers
pick off tank drivers.

247
00:39:20.501 --> 00:39:22.901
Sometimes tank drivers
pick them off first. Kaminski.

248
00:39:23.021 --> 00:39:24.301
Really?

249
00:39:26.102 --> 00:39:27.502
Grenade!

250
00:39:29.102 --> 00:39:30.421
Get down!

251
00:39:34.621 --> 00:39:36.221
Where are they?

252
00:39:52.422 --> 00:39:54.221
Grenade!

253
00:39:54.301 --> 00:39:58.301
Are you all right. Golikov?

254
00:39:58.421 --> 00:40:02.021
- Open the hatch!
- I'm gettin' fucking slaughtered down here!

255
00:40:02.101 --> 00:40:04.301
Open the hatch!

256
00:40:04.421 --> 00:40:07.301
I'm bleeding! I'm bleeding!

257
00:40:12.622 --> 00:40:14.502
- Inside!
- Get inside.

258
00:40:14.622 --> 00:40:17.101
Get in the tank. Hurry up!

259
00:40:20.621 --> 00:40:23.899
Koverchenko. get us the hell outta here!

260
00:40:24.019 --> 00:40:25.420
Hurry up!

261
00:40:27.901 --> 00:40:30.398
We've got a fire on top!

262
00:40:30.421 --> 00:40:31.500
I'm dying!

263
00:40:31.620 --> 00:40:32.597
I can't see!

264
00:40:32.620 --> 00:40:33.900
I'm dying!

265
00:40:34.020 --> 00:40:35.300
Hard right!

266
00:40:38.700 --> 00:40:40.701
