301
00:44:07.019 --> 00:44:08.477
Wait a minute. I don't think they see us.

302
00:44:08.500 --> 00:44:10.197
By the way they're moving.
I don't think they see us.

303
00:44:10.220 --> 00:44:11.797
Sir. they're in effective RPG range.

304
00:44:11.820 --> 00:44:12.900
Wait a minute. wait a...

305
