381
00:52:02.897 --> 00:52:07.097
I stuffed Molotovs under. under
turret and cannon and. and...

382
00:52:07.217 --> 00:52:09.897
And they pulled me up again!
Eight years old!

383
00:52:13.617 --> 00:52:15.697
They called me Tank Boy.

384
00:52:17.817 --> 00:52:20.017
I took a lot of Nazi tanks.

385
00:52:22.617 --> 00:52:23.696
A lot.

386
00:52:27.097 --> 00:52:30.017
