460
00:56:45.016 --> 00:56:47.895
Golikov! God damn it!

461
00:56:48.015 --> 00:56:50.215
Anthony. Gol...

462
00:56:50.295 --> 00:56:52.192
Golikov!

463
00:56:52.215 --> 00:56:54.614
